metadata.name: FOMO Card #1/1000
metadata.description:
This card inspired by Marseille tarot deck. 
 
This card named Puppeteer. And this puppeteer is FOMO, and you are its puppet. This card symbolizes a tendency to spontaneous momentary and rash decisions. It may seem like you can't change the situation, but think of it as a chance to renew yourself and chart a path that will help you become a better version of yourself. 
 
When the Puppeteer card is reversed, it suggests that you have a strong will, you clearly know your goal and strive for it. The situation is under your control. 
 
Holding this card reminds to owner that being a puppet is his own choice. This card helps to control owner's FOMO.
